{
  "texts": [
    "The complexity of APIs, which often involve diverse protocols, data formats, and domain-specific parameters, poses unique challenges.",
    "Therefore, there is a growing need to further research into the performance of LLMs in API retrieval scenarios.",
    "Such research would help identify the limitations of current models and refine their ability to accurately select and structure API calls, ultimately making these tools more adaptable to real-world applications.",
    "B. Synthetis Data GenerationTo effectively evaluate LLMs' capabilities in these complex tasks, task-specific datasets tailored to the context of API retrieval are essential.",
    "Synthetic data generation has become a widely adopted approach in domains where real-world data is either scarce or sensitive."
  ]
}